data.description: Looking for a wonderfully well priced and updated home in an established neighborhood? At just under 1,900 sq ft, this 3 bed, 2 bed, 2 car garage home offers plenty of space perfect for first time home buyer or investors. Featuring an open concept kitchen and living room with a fireplace; perfect for year-round comfort. A bonus family room can serve as an office or an extra bedroom with little work needed for the upgrade, adding to the home's flexibility. Outside, a covered patio awaits for relaxation and entertainment, complemented by two individual sheds ideal for a workshop or extra storage. Conveniently located near TTU, LCU, and the Medical District, this home offers easy access to essential amenities. Contact your agent to request a tour today!
